add four tablespoons of oil in the cake mix with half a cup of water.
Mix them well till you get a fine consistency
Then bake the cake in any mould you want and make sure to coat the mould with oil or butter.
let the cake bake for 45 minutes.
take your whipping cream and whip it with a hand mixer or a stand mixer till you get a fluffy consistency.
make the designs from the chocolate compound for decorating the cake.
when the cake is baked, decorate it with cream and chocolate however you like.
